name: The Man Who Fell to Earth (stardust)
description:
"Stardust: We Are All Made of Stars" version. 

This work was created specifically for the Collectors of objkt #195344, which was a celebration of reaching 666 Twitter Followers @LimnDigital.

In the original, #195344, we find the Traveler (a manipulated self-portrait) dusty, desolate, & colorless after crashing to Earth.

I reworked the original specifically to show the Traveler as they actually appear in the Universe...separate but as one with the Stars.
Full of Stars.
We are made of Stars.
Stars are made of Us.


3600px x 3600px x 300dpi
Minted 14 August 2021 via limnGIFTs.tez, a work by LimnDigital.tez
Twitter @LimnDigital
